description:
Version 8.0.27, the queries are giving "BIGINT UNSIGNED value is out of range" when comparing inequality results with negative whole numbers.

These work fine:
mysql> select (2 < 3) * -1.0;
-1.0

mysql> select (2 < 3) * 1;
1

This gives error:
mysql> select (2 < 3) * -1;
BIGINT UNSIGNED value is out of range
How to repeat:
SELECT (2 < 3) * -1;
